- **Disposition (drafter):** Pending challenge.
- **Dual-validation (high-assurance/control-plane):** SOL design-review verdict and rounds: pending. Claude verdict: pending. Unresolved disagreement escalates to operator.
- **Authorization:** Pending authorized-revision digest, authorizer, and date. Any silent post-authorization edit voids authorization.
- **Completion reconciliation:** Pending; record followed / authorized-deviation / unauthorized-deviation after all three dispatches.
